# packages/ui (@workspace/ui)

- This package holds **design-system atoms** (shadcn/Radix + Tailwind). Keep components **presentational** when possible; push app-specific wiring to `apps/web`.
- **Exports** are declared in `package.json` (`components/*`, `lib/*`, `globals.css`). Add new component files under `src/components/` and ensure export paths stay consistent.
- **Theming:** `src/styles/globals.css` — Tailwind v4 `@source` includes app paths; changing sources or theme tokens may affect `apps/web`.
- **CLI:** new shadcn pieces are added via the monorepo workflow in root `README.md` (typically `-c apps/web` targeting this package).
